 a few are\nbest explained as closely co-aligned field stars. Revised planet properties are\nderived for each candidate and validated planet, including cases where the\nclose neighbors are the potential host stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Nov 2014 17:27:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Nov 2014 19:27:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
