e as a\nbenchmark for future observations and models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Nov 2014 21:21:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Feb 2015 22:06:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
