pproach to\nquadratic Hamiltonians including phase conjugation which is related to time\nreversal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Nov 2014 00:25:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Nov 2014 11:02:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-27"}
