rmance. Moreover,three real world applications for which IQFRL\nplays a central role are also presented: path and objecttracking with static\nand moving obstacles avoidance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Nov 2014 13:11:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
